<div class="title">A Mellow Hit of Acid</div>
<div class="substance">2C-I</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Alex&Exact=1">Alex</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Alex. "A Mellow Hit of Acid: An Experience with 2C-I (exp42067)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Mar 4, 2008. erowid.org/exp/42067</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" border="0">
<tr><td></td><td width="15">&nbsp;</td></tr>
</table>

